I"K<p><em>Feeling Responsive</em> shows metadata by default. The default behaviour can be changed via <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">config.yml</code>. To show metadata at the end of a page/post just add the following to front matter:
<!--more--></p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>show_meta: true
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>If you don’t want to show metadata, it’s simple again:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>show_meta: false
</code></pre></div></div>

